'''履螺屬'''（學名：''{{lang|la|Crepidula}}''）是[[海螺|海螺]]的一[[屬|屬]]，屬於[[舟螺科|舟螺科]]的[[海洋生物|海洋]][[腹足纲|腹足纲]][[软体动物|软体动物]]{{r|WoRMS_137722}}。

履螺屬可能是舟螺科下最為人所知的一屬。其下多個物種在發育、生態及行為方面都有不少研究<ref>Henry, Jonathan J.; Collin, Rachel; Perry, Kimberly J.. 2010. The Slipper Snail, Crepidula: An emerging Lophotrochozoan model system. Biological Bulletin, 218(3): 211-229.</ref>。
它們一直是海洋無脊椎動物{{link-en|突發性別轉變|protandrous sex-change}}研究的主要焦點，並已用於證明性別轉變可經由環境介導的（性別變化的時間取決於與其他螺體的關聯）<ref>Mérot, Claire; Collin, Rachel. 2012. Effects of food availability on sex change in two species of Crepidula (Gastropoda: Calyptraeidae). Marine Ecology Progress Series, 449: 173-181.</ref><ref>Collin, Rachel; McLellan, Michelle; Gruber, Karl F.; Bailey-Jourdain, Catherine. 2005. Effects of Conspecific Associations on Size at Sex Change in Three Species of Calyptraeid Gastropods. Marine Ecology Progress Series, 1: 89-97.</ref><ref>Collin, Rachel. 1995. Sex, size, and position: a test of models predicting size at sex change in the protandrous gastropod crepidula fornicata. The American Naturalist, 146(6): 815-831.</ref>。
[[大西洋舟螺|大西洋舟螺]]及[[拖鞋舟螺|拖鞋舟螺]]最常用於海洋棲息地的[[入侵物種|入侵物種]]的研究<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Coe, Wesley R.|year=1948|title=Nutrition and sexuality in protandric gastropods of the genus ''Crepidula''|journal=Biol. Bul.|volume=94|issue=3|pages=158-60}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Hendler, G. and D. R. Franz|year=1971|title=Population dynamics and life history of ''Crepidula convexa'' Say (Gastropoda: Prosobranchia) in Delaware Bay|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_biological-bulletin_1971-12_141_3/page/514|journal=Biol. Bul.|volume=141|pages=514-26}}</ref>

